Doppelganger domain flodraulic-group.com, fraudulent requests for info about financial data:
'We are experiencing delays in our accounts reconciliations and with all aging receivables. This has created a bottleneck in our payment process. We need to ensure that all due invoices are paid promptly. Could you please provide an update on the payments for this period and our upcoming invoices?'

Phishing Alert

Your web site: https://tzuchipreschool.id/
server ip: 84.32.84.32

The site has been hacked and contains a special redirect for Google bot IPs. Normal visitors see normal content, but Google bots are redirected.

The domain uses naming, logos, and images infringing on slotday's trademarked name to host a fake page risking people, assets, customers, operations, and reputation.

Due to suspicious URL substring matches and appearance, the domain attempts to illegitimately impersonate slotday.

This page may harvest credentials, spread malware, or commit internet crimes. Please investigate and take action.

Urgently fix your site!

Violations:
1. The domain copies the look and feel of the official brand site and illegally uses "slotday" in its domain.
2. Brand name "slotday" appears throughout the site content.
3. Brand logos, texts, and images are stolen from the official site.
4. Illegal use of brand license.
